Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:4000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
   "task": {
     "title": "3rd Task",
     "completed": false
   }
}

